text: Alejandro Díaz (24 November 1924 - 21 October 2002) was a Cuban gymnast. He competed in eight events at the 1948 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1924 births Category:2002 deaths Category:Cuban male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Cuba Category:Gymnasts at the 1948 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Havana Category:Cuban emigrants to Puerto Rico
